# List extreme navigation

`M-up` and `M-down` jump to the first and last selectable rows in the session
list. The top spacer for an unavailable new session is not selectable, while a
valid new-session row is selectable.

    :bins jj cat

> [!NOTE]
> 'jj', and 'cat' are available.

    :copy tests/fixtures/jjconfig.toml .jjconfig.toml (copied)

    :t rename-session -t 0 runner (success)
    :t new-session -d -s beta "cat" (success)
    :t new-session -d -s delta "cat" (success)
    :t new-session -d -s ta "cat" (success)
    :t new-session -d -s zeta "cat" (success)
    :t new-session -d -s ui "sesh" (success)
    :t resize-window -t ui:0 -x 100 -y 12 (success)
    :pane ui:0.0
    :settle (settled)

Hide the preview so the session list has enough room to show several entries.
With no query, the top row is an unselectable spacer; `M-down` jumps to the
last row and `M-up` jumps back to the first selectable session.

    :k C-p
    :snap

```terminal
session:                                                                                           ┃
  6/6 | [C-r] repo: none | [C-x] close                                                             ┃
                                                                                                   ┃
▌⬤ beta                                                                                            ┃
 ⬤ delta                                                                                           ┃
 ⬤ runner                                                                                          ┃
 ⬤ ta                                                                                              ┃
 ⬤ ui                                                                                              ┃
 ⬤ zeta                                                                                            ┃
                                                                                                   ┃
                                                                                                   ┃
                                                                                                   ┃
```

![light](list-extreme-navigation.md.snap.1.light.svg)
![dark](list-extreme-navigation.md.snap.1.dark.svg)

